section.section:
Of the seven members:
One shall be employed by the Department;
One shall be employed by the Department of Natural Resources;
Three shall be licensed marine contractors and shall include:
One from Anne Arundel, Calvert, Charles, Prince George's, or St. Mary's counties;
One from Baltimore City, or Baltimore, Cecil, Harford, Kent, or Queen Anne's counties; and
One from Caroline, Dorchester, Somerset, Talbot, Wicomico, or Worcester counties; and
Two shall be private citizens, appointed at large, who represent diverse interests, and shall include:
One from Baltimore City, or Anne Arundel, Baltimore, Calvert, Charles, Harford, Prince George's, or St. Mary's counties; and
One from Caroline, Cecil, Dorchester, Kent, Queen Anne's, Somerset, Talbot, Wicomico, or Worcester counties.
